subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
To promote technical and economic cooperation with other countries, especially developing countries, to meet global challenges
- the Project will assist the growth of economic and technical cooperation between China and Africa, and encourage a public-private partnership through the creation of a China Africa Business Council (CABC)
subproject.title: China-Africa Business Council
